{"tid":516920,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"若離於愛者，無憂亦無怖。","createTime":"2018-01-01T21:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T22:23:56.000Z","uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0620b87d808ef7947bdffa75e2b32352015c1bc2","tid":516920,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T21:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a6754c736811c2f943b56a6bff5db70675e479","tid":516920,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T21:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b84999ccdccc3d70c43aaff1006ea5b941ddc5c","tid":516920,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T21:20:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab1186a4a769903e1d521eb2b502768c0bf65a14","tid":516920,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T21:46:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76ea67e11e1c511d89574207cf52c56833e4863d","tid":516920,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1186a4a769903e1d521eb2b502768c0bf65a14","tid":516920,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T21:46:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T22:18:29.000Z","msg":"「（郭襄）正出神間，忽聽得碑林旁樹叢後傳出一陣鐵鏈噹啷之聲，一人誦念佛經：『是時藥叉共王立要，即於無量百千萬億大眾之中，說勝妙伽他曰：由愛故生憂，由愛故生怖；若離於愛者，無憂亦無怖&hellip;&hellip;』郭襄聽了這四句偈言，不由得痴了，心中默默念道：『由愛故生憂，由愛故生怖；若離於愛者，無憂亦無怖。』只聽得鐵鏈拖地和念佛之聲漸漸遠去。郭襄低聲道：『我要問他，如何才能離於愛，如何能無憂無怖？』」"},{"pid":"eb6cf43ffff0aa07fb93b5bd367420b16961c25f","tid":516920,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T22:23:56.000Z","msg":"屌你啦"}]}